{"tid":1534081,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"要攬炒，就要全力搵香港無自治權、港府受北京操控既證據","createTime":"2019-09-03T01:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:14:24.000Z","uid":46933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8b12487d299e38721c11613e30efacec6cdbc8ae","tid":1534081,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"美國係唔會因為黑警殺左幾多人就檢討關係法<br />\n佢地要既係香港無自治權既有力證據<br />\n咁先有理由取消關係法<br />\n<br />\n睇下建制派去美國遊說d咩就知<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476907-20190826.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476907-20190826.htm&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=856fc817\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476907-20190826.htm&h=c3dd0fc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476907-20190826.htm</a><br />\n自由黨鍾國斌表示，在討論中，美方有提到可能要對1992年的香港政策法重新檢視。對於有美國國會議員正草擬香港人權與民主法案，新民黨葉劉淑儀認為，有部分美國國會議員不太<strong>了解香港和中國的分別</strong>，會面中有向美方解釋，<strong>稱香港仍享有高度自治和民主</strong>，而逃犯條例修訂工作已經停止。<br />\n<br />\n睇下路透社喺記者會問林鄭d咩?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e1OYE7apWgA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3De1OYE7apWgA&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=56afff71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e1OYE7apWgA</a><br />\n都係不斷追問自治權既問題<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190830/59990230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190830%2F59990230&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=40ef0d0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190830%2F59990230&h=66b2549d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190830/59990230</a><br />\n路透社: 中共最高層否決撤回修例 令林鄭不得回應任何訴求<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521041/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521041/page/1</a><br />\n《環球時報》發表社評，指路透社「林鄭月娥提交報告遭北京拒絕」是「假新聞」。<br />\n01 link唔post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【逃犯條例】環時：路透社編造謠言挑撥離間 煽動示威者對抗中央<br />\n<br />\n再到今日既林鄭錄音流出，重點講乜? 北京唔俾辭職、北京唔出解放軍、北京無定死線<br />\n<br />\n因為路透社係西方代言人，依d先係佢地眼中既政治核彈，無依d材料，黑警殺幾多人佢地都好難做野，只要港府係自己決定殺既，美國無藉口介入，乜都做唔到<br />\n有心有力既，喺送頭俾黑警之餘，去搵北京介入既證據，去搵何妖d文件通話紀錄、去搵政府內部文件、去搵大陸俾警隊既order<br />\n依d先係香港需要既政治核彈!!!"},{"pid":"0a40f8c2e06604b0021bb00def3d795d83f51d1f","tid":1534081,"uid":98141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:51:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fc8b3e52582f8952ea88e48384c06b95e8df93f5","tid":1534081,"uid":207648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a243b6c9bd7b27b92599a55d244e76e35aea915f","tid":1534081,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:05:50.000Z","msg":"林鄭段錄音咪係人證"},{"pid":"888b330cf204896ae2e1e59cd81c157ad6678933","tid":1534081,"uid":130898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:07:12.000Z","msg":"林鄭根本解釋唔到點解錄音話辭但出到黎就話冇辭<br />\n錄音已經夠料做鳩支那 <br />\n煲大佢啦"},{"pid":"939944e0ceccbcc20bb90ae88022a2f0684fb798","tid":1534081,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a243b6c9bd7b27b92599a55d244e76e35aea915f","tid":1534081,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:05:50.000Z","msg":"林鄭段錄音咪係人證"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:25:53.000Z","msg":"絕對係<br />\n對林鄭自己都有利<br />\n少d北京壓力根本對每一個做官既都有利"},{"pid":"01f45b60d100906448ea8e12ec7236dc842909b0","tid":1534081,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:14:24.000Z","msg":"【教學】將Facebook/Youtube 影片文宣轉換成Twitter 文宣<br />\n<a href=\